{
  "stem": "11671.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never heard of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we got there, we saw the sign that said, 'Arbeit macht frei.' And I remember reading it, because we knew-- our Yiddish was very similar to German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we read it and said, gee, it can't be that bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It says work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if you work hard, you're going to be free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we just thought we were going to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And immediately we were pushed, you know, to the left and to the right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my, my mother was pushed to one side with the older people, even though she was just 40-- she was 47.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And 47 in those days was very old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she was pushed to one side and-- with, with older people, and young people who were carrying their children on their arms, because the Germans didn't want to separate the mother from the child and create a scene.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they just pushed the young people who were carrying little babies to one side with the older people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my brother and my father went to another side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my two sisters and I went to one side where the working people went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, it was just mobs of people and soldiers all around us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Polish workers with the striped uniforms were, were shouting orders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and the Germans with the guns standing by some of the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think one of the soldiers later, we thought-- my sister and I thought that it was Mengele because he wore the black shiny boots and with his cane.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
